# RatingGroup

An interactive or read-only star rating widget. Supports whole-number and half-star
increments. When interactive, it behaves as a composite keyboard widget (radio group or
slider).

## 1. State Machine

### 1.1 States

| State                       | Description                               |
| --------------------------- | ----------------------------------------- |
