| Part          | Element                 | Key Attributes                                                                                              |
| ------------- | ----------------------- | ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| `Root`        | `<div>`                 | `data-ars-disabled`, `data-ars-readonly`                                                                    |
| `Label`       | `<label>`               | `data-ars-scope="rating-group"` `data-ars-part="label"`                                                     |
